                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> PoG armor is the suck.  I know I got some.  SS armor is the best for a Necro (more +HP/+INT/+Mana/Better SV stats and higher AC).  But the faction takes forever to get.  You think FD will just clear the agro like that Lol  The minute another tick goes by, the mob is once again mad at you.  Chaining Deflux on the mob to get back to 100% health alone will get you summoned.  Sitting on a mob that has you on it's hate list will get you summoned.  Renew bones is not enough healing power to keep pet alive because it has too long of a recast.  You can't afford to give your HPs to you pet.  In order to do that efficiently, you need to keep Manaskin up to absorb the damage.  That costs ~10pp a cast; too expensive.  Plus, casting manaskin while a mob is agro to you is just ALOT more agro (ask you Epic wizzy friends hehe).<br /><br />Get a group and kill them, that way after you get your lock of banshee hair you can stick around for more experience.  The risk vs. reward is not worth it IMHO.</span id="msg"></font></td>
